## Change 3: Replace Manual Transaction in `project-aliases.ts`

**Problem:** `setProjectAliases` uses `db.exec("BEGIN TRANSACTION")` / `db.exec("COMMIT")` / `db.exec("ROLLBACK")` manually, unlike every other file in the codebase which uses `db.transaction()()`.

**Solution:** Replace with `db.transaction()()`:

```typescript
// Before:
db.exec("BEGIN TRANSACTION");
try {
  db.query("DELETE FROM project_aliases").run();
  // ...inserts...
  db.exec("COMMIT");
} catch (error) {
  db.exec("ROLLBACK");
  throw error;
}

// After:
db.transaction(() => {
  db.query("DELETE FROM project_aliases").run();
  // ...inserts...
})();
```

**Files modified:**
- `src/lib/db/project-aliases.ts` — Replace manual transaction (~5 lines saved)

**Estimated savings:** ~5 lines removed

**Tests to verify:**
```bash
bun test test/lib/db/model-based.test.ts  # Alias commands in model-based tests
```

